{{Quote|This is my ship, I run it my way, and I don't need any advice from freeloading goof-offs. Got it?|Jes|<ref name="SFTE" />}}
'''Jes' courier ship''' served as [[Jes (courier)|Jes]]' personal [[Courier/Legends|courier]] whle she served with the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. As most courier ships it was built for speed, not for comfortable voyage.<ref name="SFTE">''[[Dark Forces: Soldier for the Empire]]''</ref>

By [[1 BBY/Legends|1 BBY]] it was stationed on the ''[[New Hope]]'' and Jes took [[Jan Ors]] to [[Danuta]] within four [[Standard day/Legends|days]], one day before a conventional [[Freighter/Legends|freigher]].<ref name="SFTE" />

